Wipeng: was that your first game? The ext-### games are the 24-hour games (so like this, but every phase (day/night) is 12 hours)
they are hosted by the side moderators, aiming for around 1 or 2 active at a time
The other games (eg, SMC-###, VMH-###) are what we call "player-hosted" games - they are "speed" games (either 4mins/1min day/night, or 8/2, or 10/5)
The ext games play the exact same way these do, but regularly and slower. The speed games play whenever there is enough people around who are interested and someone decides to start one
